<MudContainer MaxWidth="MaxWidth.False" Class="mt-4">
    <MudPaper Class="pa-4">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h4" GutterBottom="true">Project Overview</MudText>

        <MudText Class="mb-3">
            Our team has partnered with Strength Technologies LLC to transform their innovative "Force Rack" technology from a specialized weight-room training tool into a fully functional, commercial-style arcade experience. By harnessing the Force Rack's load cell technology—which converts a user's isometric physical force into digital data—we have designed and built a standalone, multi-game arcade cabinet driven entirely by physical exertion.
        </MudText>

        <MudText Class="mb-3">
            This project requires a robust blend of application design, embedded systems programming, and hardware integration to deliver a production-ready arcade machine. Key technical achievements include:
        </MudText>

        <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
            <li><MudText Class="mb-1"><strong>Unified Arcade Ecosystem:</strong> A custom-built software suite and launcher that allows users to seamlessly navigate and play a variety of engaging, physical video games.</MudText></li>
            <li><MudText Class="mb-1"><strong>Comprehensive Hardware Integration:</strong> Processing real-time physical data by bridging Arduino-driven load cells with a central computer. The system integrates traditional arcade controls, custom LED lighting feedback, and commercial payment hardware.</MudText></li>
            <li><MudText Class="mb-1"><strong>Persistent User Experience:</strong> A shared services architecture that handles real-time sensor polling, centralized game settings, and persistent local leaderboards to drive competition.</MudText></li>
        </ul>

        <MudText>
            By the end of this project, we will deliver a complete, highly engaging arcade cabinet that proves the exciting potential of physical, force-based gaming and successfully expands the True Force technology into the interactive entertainment market.
        </MudText>
    </MudPaper>
</MudContainer>